                <button class="faq-question">
                    <span>What is 48 Roots?</span>
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>48 Roots is a Palestinian-inspired apparel brand that combines modern fashion with cultural heritage. The name "48 Roots" refers to 1948, a significant year in Palestinian history. Every purchase directly supports Palestinian families and relief organizations.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question">
                    <span>How much of my purchase goes to Palestine?</span>
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>We donate a fixed amount from every purchase to verified Palestinian relief organizations. This donation amount is displayed at checkout and on your order confirmation.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question">
                    <span>How long does shipping take?</span>
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                </button>
